 $\\mathscr{M}$ and its `rough'\n(Legendre) dual $\\tilde{\\mathscr{M}}$. The lower bounds, demonstrating the\nsharpness of the result in several cases, follow from a combination of harmonic\nanalysis techniques and the geometry of numbers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 May 2023 19:21:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
