ining their unique qualities, teachers, students, and\nuniversities can effectively navigate the integration of AI, ensuring a\nwell-rounded and impactful learning experience.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 May 2023 03:39:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
