pprox -0.6991$ and $-0.6949$\nfor $CC + Pantheon^{+}$ and $\\omega\\approx -0.7001$ and $-0.7084$ for $CC +\nPantheon^{+} + BAO$ respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 May 2023 05:24:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-02"}
